 ではまず、裸を意味するbirthday suitを使ってこちらのセンテンス。

90
00:06:48,643 --> 00:06:52,643
 Nihon dewa itsumo hadaka de onsen ni hairimasu.

91
00:06:59,123 --> 00:07:04,863
 In Japan, people usually go in hot springs in their birthday suits.

92
